@startuml seq_27_assign_roles
title Sequence Diagram: UC-27 Assign Roles

actor Owner
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Role Controller" as Controller
participant "Role Service" as Service
participant "Community Repo" as Repo
participant "Event Bus\n(Go Channels)" as EventBus

Owner -> Frontend: Invite member as Moderator
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/communities/{id}/roles {user_id, role: "moderator"}
Controller -> Service: Assign Role
Service -> Repo: Validate creator/owner permissions
Repo --> Service: Permissions valid

Service -> Repo: Insert moderator invitation/assignment record
Repo --> Service: Record created

Service -> EventBus: Publish RoleAssignedEvent
note right of EventBus
  Background goroutine notifies
  the target user
end note

Service -> Repo: Fetch updated role list
Repo --> Service: Role list
Service --> Controller: Updated Role List
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> Owner: Refresh role management UI
@enduml